metadata.title: Wireless Bluetooth Earbuds, Bluetooth 5.3 in-Ear Headphones,3D Stereo IPX6 sweatproof, Entertainment time Charging Box, Noise Reduction Mini Earbuds, Built-in Microphone for iOS and Android Device
features: 【Bluetooth 5.3 & Easy To Pair】: With the most advanced Bluetooth V5.3 technology you are getting 2x faster transmission speed and more stable connectivity without signal loss or music dropouts; Pick up 2 headsets from charging box, they will connect each other automatically, then only one step easily set mobile phone Bluetooth to pair the earbuds.

【Wireless Charging Technology】With highly effective wireless charging case equipped, wireless earphones simplify all the charging process and deliver the truth wireless life experiences. Charging just as easy as placing them on the charging pad. Lay it down, charge it up, just like magic.

【Sport Fit Design & Touch Control】 With ergonomic and sport redesign, Bluetooth earbuds can fit and stay secured in ear canal even with intense movement. Together with smart touch sensors, without using the phone and largely prevent the discomfort like the physical button.

【8H Ultra-long Playtime】With wireless headphones, you can bring them anywhere without the concern of battery life. Leave alone they can last 8H [2 Times longer than other earbuds]. The portable wireless charging case can recharge the earbuds 5 times when they sit on the case and accumulate the playtime up to 30H. Free to enjoy multiple movies, series, dramas, gaming and hundred songs that will never stop!
【IPX6 Sweat Water-Resistant】：The true wireless earbuds against damage from sweat or rain; It won't get in the way of enjoying sports, music and calls; Perfect for fitness, travelling, etc.
description: The Y10 Mini Wireless Headphone is smaller than other headphone brands and ergonomically designed for long-lasting, pain-free use. The best option for work, travel and sports.
Our wireless headphones use the latest Bluetooth V5.3 EDR and TWS technology for stronger signals, faster pairing, and more stable transmission.
Supports automatic power on / off, automatic pairing, automatic charging and other functions. They are very clear.
Compared to other brands of headphones, our wireless headphones are smaller, more comfortable, more ergonomic and can be used for a long time without pain.
Stereo speaker and music playing are the best choice for car driving and sports.
